DELETE FROM "umbracoOpenIddictTokens" AS "u"
WHERE "u"."Id" IN (
    SELECT "u0"."Id"
    FROM "umbracoOpenIddictTokens" AS "u0"
    LEFT JOIN "umbracoOpenIddictAuthorizations" AS "u1" ON "u0"."AuthorizationId" = "u1"."Id"
    WHERE "u0"."CreationDate" < @__date_0 AND ((("u0"."Status" <> 'inactive' OR "u0"."Status" IS NULL) AND ("u0"."Status" <> 'valid' OR "u0"."Status" IS NULL)) OR ("u1"."Id" IS NOT NULL AND ("u1"."Status" <> 'valid' OR "u1"."Status" IS NULL)) OR "u0"."ExpirationDate" < rtrim(rtrim(strftime('%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%f', 'now'), '0'), '.'))
    ORDER BY "u0"."Id"
    LIMIT @__p_1
)

DELETE FROM "umbracoOpenIddictAuthorizations" AS "u"
WHERE "u"."Id" IN (
    SELECT "u0"."Id"
    FROM "umbracoOpenIddictAuthorizations" AS "u0"
    WHERE "u0"."CreationDate" < @__date_0 AND ("u0"."Status" <> 'valid' OR "u0"."Status" IS NULL OR "u0"."Type" = 'ad-hoc') AND NOT EXISTS (
        SELECT 1
        FROM "umbracoOpenIddictTokens" AS "u1"
        WHERE "u0"."Id" = "u1"."AuthorizationId")
    ORDER BY "u0"."Id"
    LIMIT @__p_1
)
